{{About|the documentary series|the drama series|Notorious (2016 TV series)}}
{{infobox television | | show_name = Notorious | image = Notorious bio logo.png | caption = | runtime = 42 minutes | creator = | starring = | opentheme = | endtheme = | language = English | country = United States | network = [[The Biography Channel]] | first_aired = September 27, 2004 | last_aired = December 14, 2007 | num_seasons = 4 | genre = [[Documentary film|Documentary]] | num_episodes = 152 | website = }} '''''Notorious''''' is an American [[Documentary film|documentary]] television series that profiles the lives of infamous individuals in history. The series aired on [[The Biography Channel]].
Most episodes of ''Notorious'' are rehashes of the similar television shows ''[[American Justice]]'' and ''[[Mobsters (TV series)|Mobsters]]'', both series that were originally broadcast on [[A&E Network|A&E]], Biography Channel's sister channel. The only difference between the series is the introduction of the episodes and the lead-in after commercials.
